Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:56.65,OP_CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)}「看着我」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.29,OP_CN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(200,200)}「快察觉我对你的感情」
